e as he tried standing again after being drug most of the way. <br>
<br>
&quot;You will pay for this witch!&quot; He hissed as Solari dismounted. <br>
<br>
No words were said on her part as she walked over to him and head-butted him, knocking him unconscious. She turned around, seeing Hippolyte standing by the fire. Walking over, she lifted up her mask, then knelt infront of her cousin.<br>
<br>
&quot;Good to see you my queen.&quot; Solari said softly and respectfully. &quot;I am grateful to the gods for your safe return.&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daughterofshylock>Daughter of Shylock</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 394<br> <font color=#993300>(5/12/03 6:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=225>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ....</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded reaching down to a pot of cleaning water and wrung out a small cloth handing it to Hippolyte. She stopped as another request was given and smiled.<br>
