&quot;Here. Take this.&quot; she handed her a small black vile. &quot;Drink it all in one gulp, it tastes like Centaur blood,&quot; meaning it tastes like crap. &quot;But it'll kill any pain from a mortal wound, labor, to a paper cut.&quot; She smirked lightly.<br>
<br>
It was called Wolves Blood, Alysia's greatest invention. She created it along with Sariah back in Scynthia from herbs that only grew in her lands. And it worked better than any mortal medication known.<br>
