<br>
Alysia nodded to Hippolyte and spoke in a whisper so the others could not hear her among the camp.<br>
<br>
&quot;I agree, slaves in an amazon city are not well to do with. However, I'll take those three.&quot; Points to the ones that the wolves guard.<br>
<br>
&quot;If you all would like to come to Scynthia to see them disposed of, you're more than welcome.&quot; She smiled softly and then turned to Odessa.<br>
<br>
&quot;Of course Odessa, in fact, you can have one for yourself if you'd like.&quot; Alysia grinned and then looked to the wovles and Tahira.<br>
<br>
&quot;Those who go to Scynthia, we leave now. I want to get through the gates before the melting snow from the mountains floods the rivers.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked back to the other Queens.<br>
<br>
&quot;If there's no further need of me here. . . &quot;<br>
She said in mroe of a question than a statement. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solariwolf@amazonsunite>solariwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Themiscryian War Queen</span><br>  Posts: 220<br> <font color=#993300>(5/19/03 7:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=235>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Solari sat there, seemingly in a trance by the firelight flicking. Her mind still racing from the attack earlier. The pain from her wounds was now pounding, as she looked down to see her freshly seared wounds, glowing red. She sighed softly as the pain shook thru her body, then reached around to search for something inside her pouch on her belt. Pulling out a small vile, she pulled the cork out and drank down the liquid. It was cool and sweet going down her throat. <br>
&quot;Who is going to take first watch tonight?&quot; She asked looking up at those around the fire. &quot;I do not wish to be awakend with a sword to my throat by one of these prisoners.&quot; Her glance was cast in the direction of the Roman commander she had tied up.<br>
The food that was being prepared was beginning to smell really tempting. Solari had not eaten in some time now, her mind had been elsewhere.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alexiares>Alexiares</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 34<br> <font color=#993300>(5/22/03 10:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=236>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/queenhippolyte/images/alexiares.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Attack is over</span><hr size=1> Finishing her cooking, Alexiares drained the water from the wild foods.   She stood up holding the pot with a bit of her skirt to keep her hands from burning.  Looking to the queens, Alexiares had always been taught to offer the food to royalty after offering to priestesses.  And since there were no priestesses, Alexi turned to the Queens and walked over.  She bowed her head as she neared them and offered the food with a bit of a smile.  &quot;My Vasilissa's and heroines, would you like something to eat?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Platinum Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 970<br>